Description:
Seemingly hates football and enrolled precisely
because South Cirrus Junior High has no football team.
Name: Destin Billows

Description:
Known as the school's delinquent,
he's got killer kicks and spring-loaded legs.
Name: Briar Bloomhurst

Description:
The upbeat spark who lights up any room,
and his relentless pestering? Straight-up stalker level.
Name: Cedric Freud

Description:
Cheerful, charming, and everyone's favorite, she's always
chasing the next thrill, more into the climb than the summit.
Name: Raika Shinohara

Description:
Gentle by nature and quick on his feet, but when
pressure hits, he curls up like a turtle.
Name: Cade Shelby

Description:
A rule-stickler with a rock-solid sense of duty.
His reflexes? Sharpened to perfection through
cutthroat card battles.
Name: Alix La Fontaine

Description:
Towering at 190cm with a presence that commands the pitch,
he's a born boss who never fades into the background.
Name: Thierry Reyes

Description:
He lives for competition and challenges anyone anywhere,
except ghosts, those still freak him out.
Name: Winsor Compete

Description:
Born into Kabuki and raised on drama, he charges into
every match like he's living out a role like possessed.
Name: Charis Benzaie

Description:
A true mentalist, reading emotions like open books
while tracking enemy intent and tuning up team morale.
Name: Maine Alsop

Description:
He's never in a rush, never stressed.
Just climbs steadily, one step at a time.
Name: Dario Highton

Description:
She breezes through new stuff like it's dÃ©jÃ  vuâ€”
that's why they call her "Second-Playthrough Amelia."
Name: Amelia Rainwalker

Description:
She's all grace and poise on the outside.
But underneath? Nothing but raw effort.
Name: Marisol Cavallo

Description:
Honest to a fault and always polite,
she's built a loyal following, especially among the girls.
Name: Meridia Althoff

Description:
While small, speedy, and sometimes shaky,
his eye for space turns him into a pitch-reading pro.
Name: Tai Richter

Description:
A rugby-forged wrecking ball who, once he gets moving,
barrels through the midfield like a freight train.
Name: Davin Bullock

Description:
Loves illusions, lives for tricks. His gags?
So bad they drive people up the wall.
Name: Lycus Foxworth

Description:
Quiet and timid deep down, but since junior high,
he's faked being a loudmouth playboy.
Name: Florent Shorleigh

Description:
Said to bring happiness wherever she goes,
she's the team's calm, fearless, spiritual anchor.
Name: Antonia Felicier

Description:
Tough as nails and just as fearless,
he dives headfirst into everything.
Name: Kelvin Steelborne

Description:
A crafty trap-setter with a mouth to match,
his lanky frame makes him a nightmare to get past.
Name: Lemmy Stretchen

Description:
A future rock god with speed to burn,
she plays loud, fast, and totally unfiltered.
Name: Starla Thorn

Description:
Student council president, sharp as a whip,
she wins people over before they know what hit 'em.
Name: Lilac Tausend

Description:
Tech-savvy and muscle-obsessed, this
student council secretary won't for her life stop analyzing everyone.
Name: Juno Hundertmark

Description:
Always sneaking around... but secretly a top-tier
Platinum InaTuber with fans for days.
Name: Edwin Grove

Description:
Grew up rough and tough, lives by
his own rules, and fights for justice.
Name: Milo Rankin

Description:
Defender and attacker rolled into one,
crushing foes with high headers.
Name: Peake Fletcher

Description:
A fiend in defense, he stands firm
like a fortress on the pitch.
Name: Sentry Scarborough

Description:
Speedy and slick with the ball.
Darts through defences like a spear.
Name: Autry Rogers

Description:
Temple-born and trained in martial arts,
he uses unique breathing techniques on the pitch.
Name: Bodhi Field

Description:
No natural skill but huge on effort.
Never misses training.
Name: Chase Winthrop

Description:
The contrast between her noble birth
and her unrestrained football amuses many.
Name: Hawky Savard

Description:
His striking looks naturally draw eyes,
making him an easy decoy.
Name: Taliesin Greenhunt

Description:
Supports Nikas with broad insight.
Soft-spoken but strangely persuasive.
Name: Ivan Mercer

Description:
Handsome and composed, the girls
love him. Soothes the hotheaded Nikas.
Name: Erdem Barath

Description:
A striker skilled in attack and defence,
loyal to his teammates and quick to tears.
Name: Nikas Himmelstein

Description:
On the bench but sharp-eyed,
always analyzing plays with the manager.
Name: Hugh Pronghorn

Description:
Not fast but rock-solid. Plows through
defences without hesitation.
Name: Everett Shipman

Description:
Great jumper who owns the skies
and catches anything that flies.
Name: Armin Marshall

Description:
Helps the team strike as oneâ€”
like arrows from the same quiver.
Name: Conley Quiver

Description:
Prefers raw power over finesse.
His shots hit like cannon fire.
Name: Denzel Harvest

Description:
Famed for his knack to assess players.
His tactical plays hit where it hurts.
Name: Neil Turner

Description:
Gray man type who fades in
to back up the team.
Name: Raz Pond

Description:
Quiz society by day, football club by afternoon,
his lightning reflexes make him a top keeper.
Name: Dax Prescott

Description:
Strict academic parents barred him from Raimon,
and he's stayed aloof and disillusioned since.
Name: Edvan Trodden

Description:
In practice, he slides like a natural.
But come match time, he locks up.
Name: Drever Olflaire

Description:
The soft-spoken treasurer of West Manor's student council
is slow to act and would rather count coins than chase goals.
Name: Looke Raundoff

Description:
Dreams of a muscle-powered world, and spreads
his homemade Wheyston Protein like gospel.
Name: Rutheo Wheyston

Description:
Cool and collected on the surface,
until a game face from the other team makes her swoon mid-match.
Name: Ernesta Beauregard

Description:
Strict, sharp, and tactical,
he never lets a rival school get the better of him.
Name: Laymark Starwyn

Description:
He's a walking football encyclopedia.
Even knows which pro player owns which pet.
Name: Moby Tidbitt

Description:
A model student with gentlemanly charm,
and a steady backbone as the council's president.
Name: Edgard Loathe

Description:
Carefree and springy on his feet, he was scouted for sportsâ€”
but his grades are another story.
Name: Flanko Midspringle

Description:
A livestreamer who calls matches like a Let's Play,
complete with memes and hashtags.
Name: Berdy Caster

Description:
A gentle soul wants to live strong and kind,
like a wildflower holding its own by the roadside.
Name: Chicory Bellflower

Description:
Roped in by his football-manga-artist mom, and still
loudly claims he's a baseball guy out of protest.
Name: Aysen DeMacon

Description:
He once broke a family heirloom at practice.
Now he won't rest until his ball control is flawless.
Name: Breppo Terrey

Description:
Her family runs an ice cream shop, and after games
she shares homemade treats with everyone.
Name: Frie Sorbet

Description:
Joined to write football songs but fell in love with the game,
now he splits his heart between boots and chords.
Name: Eddi Losse

Description:
A warm, encouraging teacher who supports young talent,
though sometimes a bit too optimistic about their chances.
Name: Waddell Homely

Description:
A born genius who nails it first try, analyzing each player's
weak spots and training them hard.
Name: Yasmin Tausend

Description:
Son of pro players who despise Mark Evans,
he was sent to Japan to take down their rival's kid, Harper.
Name: Martino Leone

Description:
Born with razor-sharp eyes,
she reads the game like she's seeing the future.
Name: Judie Cassios

Description:
Hails from a beast-wrestling tribe,
so even the biggest bruisers just feel like kittens to him.
Name: Gigy Maharaja

Description:
Raised by the sea and trained in diving,
she hunts down opponents with tireless resolve.
Name: Jenny Okutba

Description:
A juggling pro who makes
the ball stick to his feet like magic.
Name: Robart Anderson

Description:
Starts each day meditating under a waterfall,
then spends it clashing with restless Sikuvot.
Name: Ming Chow

Description:
She glides past foes like she has wings,
earning the nickname "Angel from the Night Sky."
Name: Maribelle Flanmir

Description:
Leads with pure skill and
keeps the wild exchange students in line.
Name: Toyo Yamanouchi

Description:
A parkour ace who glides across the pitch like
a leaf on the wind, dodging foes with stunning grace.
Name: Sikuvot Shivan

Description:
Shoots cannonball-like shots that
blast defenders away and shake the net.
Name: Kai Yoshizaki

Description:
Jazz flows in his veins, while his dribbling
follows the wild beat in his head.
Name: Joey Beat

Description:
A deadly sharpshooter who hits
the goal with pinpoint precision.
Name: Olson Carchis

Description:
Running with her big dog sped him up,
and he swears his pup's the secret to his skills.
Name: Mengmeng Wang

Description:
His Muay Thai punches hit hard and
sometimes he even breaks balls when making saves.
Name: Kaos Dao

Description:
Obsessed with samurai and in the kendo club,
he strikes the ball with sweeping, sword-like kicks.
Name: Edmond Pias

Description:
He skips the first half, claiming "heroes arrive late,"
which drives his manager crazy.
Name: Kain Vijet

Description:
A part explorer, part manager who scouts worldwide
for hidden stars and shapes them up.
Name: Derrin Wilson

Description:
Fluent in several languages and built for sport,
he's the go-to guy for homesick teammates.
Name: Anita Navarro

Description:
She's a goalie who lets the dice decide her mood,
and nobody can predict what comes next.
Name: Kiona Blackwell

Description:
Well-loved and sportsmanlike, he's admired for
his integrity and devotion to his longtime girlfriend.
Name: Lennox Portsman

Description:
When he's not painting ukiyo-e,
he's hunting down openings on the pitch like a sniper.
Name: Kaz Bloomfield

Description:
Dark and fierce, he haunts opponents
by bringing out his Keshin to shake their nerves.
Name: Govin Castlehoven

Description:
Full of pride and star power,
she's got a presence that steals every spotlight.
Name: Floramira Pagotta

Description:
A viral sensation in the making,
he's always pulling flashy moves and collabs mid-match.
Name: Alistar Montero

Description:
From a storyteller's bloodline,
he binds the team tight with charm and quick wit.
Name: Elijah Singleton

Description:
His interception skills make defenders groan,
but nerves often get the best of him.
Name: Rohan Snatchett

Description:
Hurt once, he now dodges tackles with slick
timing instead of brute force.
Name: Umbren Lightwood

Description:
Sharp-tongued and deadly focused,
his footwork cuts through defences like a scalpel.
Name: Blaine Westbrook

Description:
Descended from a courier, he sticks to straight dribbles
because his Artemian-like speed is off the charts.
Name: Marinus Courier

Description:
Loyal to the core, he hums the school chant
through every play, win or lose.
Name: Zelane Whitlow

Description:
Growing up in a haunted house, he's used to ghosts
and keeps calm under the wildest pressure.
Name: Rael Abbeybogy

Description:
Moves like a proâ€”when napping.
Rumor says he's possessed by the ghost of a football legend.
Name: Dawsey Geistfeld

Description:
Silent and mysterious, he wears a fox mask and moves unseen,
stealing the ball before anyone notices.
Name: Volk Lorius

Description:
A fierce defender with a wild streak,
known for brutal heel drops and sparring wild boars
after practice.
Name: Drexel Kixley

Description:
A Keshin expert who's spent years unlocking their secrets
and builds teams led by their summoners.
Name: Wythers Moonridge

Description:
Cedric and Blaine's childhood friend and former player,
she offers sharp, hands-on support from the pitch.
Name: Mirela Delisle

Description:
His insane vision catches shots coming from impossible angles,
as he stops goals left and right.
Name: Ashlan Panoptos

Description:
The sharpest mind on the pitch,
he wins duels with smart moves and perfect timing.
Name: Hudson Headland

Description:
A provocateur who lives to rile opponents,
smirking as they fall for his traps.
Name: Vex Frieden

Description:
Climbs mountains every day to stargaze,
building strength and a jump that defies belief.
Name: Asten Royds

Description:
A brutally honest match critic on social media,
famous for sharp analysis and a massive fanbase.
Name: Ruelle Neurivieu

Description:
Keeps cool through daily sauna meditation
and plays with zen-like calm no matter the score.
Name: Theon Stillcliffe

Description:
He overlooks weaker rivals but stands strong
behind his captain when it matters most.
Name: Ciel Natcherall

Description:
A selfish striker who craves goals and
throws fits if anyone else scores first.
Name: Kaien Spiradawn

Description:
Protects his teammates like family and
never holds back when they get fouled.
Name: Kyo Seestar

Description:
The captain who reads Alice's plays immediately,
leading the squad with steady skill and calm focus.
Name: Syd Faircrest

Description:
A former sumo trainee whose massive frame
hides surprising good manners.
Name: Solan Brightmoor

Description:
A silent grinder who trains every day and
can't hold back tears when hard work pays off.
Name: Lenox Grinder

Description:
Puts assists first, hates the glory hogs,
and keeps the team moving behind the scenes.
Name: Ophelia Ennercourt

Description:
Trains daily with steel girders to build an
unbreakable body and takes hits like a fortress.
Name: Riggs Fornstrut

Description:
A young heiress raised in war tactics and manners
whose presence commands obedience.
Name: Leticia Legatus

Description:
His lightning-fast passes slice through defences
and turn crises into clear opportunities.
Name: Arran Realis

Description:
A prodigious manager with full control his team,
he predicts plays so well he's rarely challenged.
Name: Alice Rendell

Description:
Alice's right hand and strategist who's always
lost in cryptic Wonderland conversations
Name: Partis Payton

Description:
Drew a map so sharp it made the village hall wall
and now plots passes with the same precision.
Name: Hobie Chartwood

Description:
Barber's daughter with big-city perm dreams
and a clean bob that says "not yet, but soon."
Name: Lila Glosswood

Description:
A sharp school reporter who's interviewed half the village
and always digs up the enemy's weaknesses.
Name: Rowland Brightwood

Description:
A master angler who channels fishing focus
into airtight defence and knows more fish than people.
Name: Tristan Brookwood

Description:
Trained in martial arts as part of the village watch,
he's dead serious about protecting his team.
Name: Lachlan Hartwood

Description:
Born noble and polished to perfection,
she plays with elegance but her passes hit like a hammer.
Name: Nathaniel Whitewood

Description:
Hails from a hunting family and hones his aim
by trying to take out wild boars with footballs.
Name: Orin Wildwood

Description:
Oldest of six and raised to wrangle chaos,
he now runs the midfield with practiced precision.
Name: Calvin Sixwood

Description:
Tells village ghost stories with creepy flair
and sells every word like she's lived it.
Name: Iris Nightwood

Description:
Never seen without mugwort mochi in hand,
he swears it's the secret to his muscle gains.
Name: Vearn Dashwood

Description:
Polite to a fault but quietly bitter toward city types.
He sticks close to Vearn and keeps supporting him.
Name: Asher Norwood

Description:
A blunt student-athlete with zero filter and
a habit of digging holes he can't quite climb out of.
Name: Emory Plainwood

Description:
Obsessed by Noh masks, she uses her creepy smile
as a weapon to rattle opponents.
Name: Maris Hollowwood

Description:
With festival-sized stamina and grown-up muscle,
he lugs the shrine like one of the village elders.
Name: Ronan Strongwood

Description:
Grew up dashing around handing candy to tourists
and wound up with stamina that never quits.
Name: Lydia Trailwood

Description:
Sings old folk songs with a voice like home and
follows the ball by ear like it's part of the melody.
Name: Alden Songwood

Description:
Still spry at 80, Twinford's mayor pretends not to hear
when talk turns inconvenient.
Name: Theobald Longwood

Description:
A greengrocer's daughter turned civil servant,
she crunches numbers faster than most can speak.
Name: Mabel Greenwood

Description:
A rich girl obsessed with idol players who never
drops her smile, even when running on fumes.
Name: Lilia Charmont

Description:
A caring sisterly figure from a hospital family who
treats bruises gently but scolds like a drill sergeant.
Name: Evelyn Hale

Description:
A lone wolf with sharp instincts who dodges
attacks before they even happen.
Name: Elara Silvane

Description:
Sweet and clingy to her favorites,
yet ice-cold to everyone else.
Name: Margie Frostveil

Description:
A bubbly, high-energy fashionista whose flashy acrobatics
keep the crowd screaming for more.
Name: Galia Flair

Description:
Shy off the pitch, she uses self-hypnosis to flip a switch
and play using a bolder persona.
Name: Selene Trance

Description:
Called the Merciless Queen, she plays with elegant skill
and ruthless precision that shatter dreams.
Name: Elyse Reign

Description:
Built like a pro, she crushes the pitch with raw power
and muscle-driven plays.
Name: Eliza Florence

Description:
An inventor's daughter and robotics champion
who trains with robots she built herself.
Name: Adelina Gearhart

Description:
Quick to want what others have,
she loses interest the moment it's hers.
Name: Clarisse Luxe

Description:
A model born to fame who demands perfection
from her squad and twice as much from herself.
Name: Celina Lavelle

Description:
A smooth-reading socialite who keeps the peace
by always backing the majority.
Name: Amara Winslow

Description:
She gushes over cute girl moments and turns every
spark of romance into manga fuel.
Name: Liliane Alban

Description:
From a haunted mansion, she chants eerie spells
mid-match like it's totally normal.
Name: Lenora Graves

Description:
Raised by samurai, she plays with respect and follows
orders like second nature.
Name: Kiyora Asakiri

Description:
A talkative mood-maker who fires off jokes
whether they land or not.
Name: Talia Jester

Description:
A regal science teacher who rules the pitch with
strict discipline and perfect sync.
Name: Apia Crownwell

Description:
Lugs around an empty beehive and whispers to bees
that may or may not be real.
Name: Melissa Hivewood

Description:
Bright and bubbly, he dreams of befriending every rival
and throwing one huge festival for all.
Name: Mayen Harmet

Description:
A cool-headed delinquent who charms the crowd
and reads faces like open books.
Name: Vinda Koral

Description:
Easygoing and upbeat, he stumbles into miracle plays
with a style all his own.
Name: Yarkin Cittey

Description:
A straight-laced player who calls out dirty moves
and scolds teammates when they cross the line.
Name: Susen Faircourt

Description:
He's new to the sport but plays with quiet power
and a presence you can't ignore.
Name: Budan Ashwell

Description:
Shy and wary of delinquents, she trains nonstop
to avoid messing up and catching heat.
Name: Hathea Calmell

Description:
He struts with style and spotless boots,
but step on them and he snaps.
Name: Benton Zellner

Description:
Once a model student, now prickly and bitter
after being uprooted by relocation.
Name: Froclan Junn

Description:
A simple, eager seventh grader who hangs on every word
from his seniors and manager.
Name: Ebiss Marlowe

Description:
His rapid-fire kicks blur into afterimagesâ€”
no wonder they call him the Scarlet Centipede.
Name: Vashan Morell

Description:
Former Fauxshore captain whose plays with Vashan
stirred up storms and became known as the Southern Gale.
Name: Itor Sheerman

Description:
Handy with a needle, she patches uniforms on the fly
and sometimes embroiders jackets for cash.
Name: Orfreya Newcomb

Description:
A seasoned diver with lungs of steel and a pompadour
that somehow stays rock solid underwater.
Name: Trevin Seabourne

Description:
Plays to vent stress but gets banged up chasing every ball
like it's life or death.
Name: Jory Jinx

Description:
Once timid, she found her fire watching the old headmaster's
team and swore she'd never stay quiet again.
Name: Clementine Weston

Description:
A Fauxshore student who's hooked on delinquent manga
and loving the new team's rowdy vibe.
Name: Jakob Serveraw

Description:
A beloved PE teacher whose kindness gets him tricked
more often than he cares to admit.
Name: Conrado Pottinger

Description:
Graceful and thoughtful, she's the team's sweetheart
and everyone's favorite shoulder to lean on.
Name: Celeste Fairbourne

Description:
Highborn heiress who built her stamina chasing
a spoiled cat across acres of land.
Name: Terra Hillcroft

Description:
Jogging route runner and "Kool Kit" owner with lightning-fast
reflexes that leave opponents guessing.
Name: Alvaro Ventura

Description:
Yelena's childhood friend and solo diner owner
with unshakable stamina and a sharp eye for the game.
Name: Mirina Mackrell

Description:
Noodle shop owner and team captain who honed
tough defence by flagging down customers.
Name: Yelena Poplawska

Description:
South Cirrus burger boss who throws his weight around
to steal the ball and shut down plays.
Name: Pattie Whitfield

Description:
A savvy smartphone shop owner who keeps
every opponent's move wired in his sharp mind.
Name: Newman Wiford

Description:
This flashy owner of Magic Moves talks big and
runs the team like a true madonna.
Name: Sheila Threadwell

Description:
Champon noodle shop owner who tweaks every dish
with sharp eyes and skilled hands.
Name: Primavera Bluefield

Description:
Dry cleaner with eagle eyes who spots any
stain's source without missing a beat.
Name: Vera Presswell

Description:
G-Mart manager who experiments boldly
and brings fresh ideas straight to the pitch.
Name: Cinnamon Dougherty

Description:
Tough liquor store owner with barrel-lifting
strength and nerves of steel.
Name: Brandy Ryehart

Description:
Tai chi herbalist whose daily practice gives
his game a quiet power and graceful flow.
Name: He Liu

Description:
Ex-guitarist turned shop owner whose booming shots
hit like the drop at a rock concert.
Name: Gibson Forte

Description:
Clever hostess who plays mind games on the pitch
and dribbles through with fearless flair.
Name: Love Stirling

Description:
Sharp-eyed fishmonger with auction-trained reflexes and
a simmering rivalry with the local butcher.
Name: Marlin Sharkey

Description:
Don't let the gentle butcher smile fool youâ€”
he charges in like a runaway bull.
Name: Lorcan Oxfield

Description:
Chatty owner of Rai Rai Noodles who rallies his team
with fiery pep talks and big heart.
Name: Joon Kim

Description:
Yelena's ever-smiling daughter who dashes store to store
keeping the whole district running.
